name: Gold Polygon Necklace
description:
Geometric and glam meet in this gold polygon necklace.  Layers and layers of steel were melted to create the unique, faceted pendant and then the entire pendant was gold plated.  The chain is 14 karat goldfill and has a spring ring clasp.

SIZING
Pendant 3/4" in length
Chain 18"

name: Sterling Silver Cuff Bracelet - Rocks Texture
description:
Sterling silver was hand-forged to make this sturdy cuff bracelet. It was textured with a nature inspired rocks pattern then oxidized, sanded and buffed to draw attention to the texture.

JEWELRY CARE:
The cuff bracelet has been given a layer of preservation wax were added to prolong the finish, but naturally keep it away from water and chemicals.

SIZING
Bracelet measures 6 1/4" in length with approx. an additional 1" opening

name: Mixed Metal Hoop Earrings
description: In these hoop earrings mixed metals and texture are combined for a slightly rustic, industrial style. Each pair is individually handmade through traditional metalworking techniques. MATERIALS Gunmetal and antiqued brass The earwires are surgical steel SIZING Dangling length from top to bottom approx. 1 1/4" Earrings will come with free clear protective earring backs.

name: Personalized ID initial cuff bracelet
description:
Wear your initials proudly of those of someone you love with this personalized cuff bracelet. The cuff bracelet is ID style and can be stamped with any two initials you would like. The gold cuff is made of brass which I have given a soft brushed finish. The letters are also oxidized slightly so they stand out.

Your cuff will also be coated with a preservation wax to preserve the color but note that this is brass so it can patina over time to a lovely heirloom quality finish! (If you prefer the shinier state use any brass cleaner to polish it up!)


SIZING:
The total length around is about 5 3/4" around with an additional 1 1/4" opening.
The cuff measures 2 1/4" across at the widest point when laid flat. The ID section is about 1" in length.
This cuff is not recommended for larger wrists.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
